WEBVTT

49:09.897 --> 49:11.605
He has a list the size of Rhode Island

49:11.605 --> 49:13.147
and he checks it twice.

49:13.522 --> 49:15.313
If you were to try
to read that list just once,

49:15.313 --> 49:17.522
it would take you a
decade, but he does it twice.

49:17.813 --> 49:20.188
And the reason why
he's able to do any of it,

49:20.188 --> 49:23.188
is because he is Santa Claus,

49:23.563 --> 49:27.480
the one and only, and no
one else can execute his mission.

49:29.522 --> 49:29.897
Which is?

49:30.230 --> 49:31.647
To spread cheer, asshole.

49:32.772 --> 49:33.605
Good feeling.

49:37.772 --> 49:38.605
Ready for a test.
